Project License Notice
======================

This repository contains:
1) Build/tooling code in this repository (scripts, Makefile, styles, plist metadata).
2) Dictionary source data obtained from external providers.

The legal terms for (2) are not overridden by this repository.

Data License Summary (Important)
--------------------------------
The lexical data pipeline depends on Icelandic lexical resources distributed under
Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International
(CC BY-NC-ND 4.0), including resources provided through CLARIN Iceland / Árnastofnun.

Under CC BY-NC-ND 4.0 in this context, you must treat generated dictionary bundles
as derivative outputs of the licensed data.

Practical compliance guidance:
- Allowed: local/private building and personal usage with attribution.
- Not allowed: redistributing modified source data.
- Not allowed: redistributing compiled dictionary bundles produced from ND data.
- Not allowed: commercial use where restricted by the source license.

You are responsible for verifying current terms at the original data source.
If source licensing changes, update this notice and your distribution behavior.

