Attribution Notes
-----------------
- Lexical source material is attributed to Stofnun Árna Magnússonar í íslenskum fræðum
  and/or the relevant CLARIN Iceland source records.
- Morphological enrichment is performed through BÍN access provided by the `islenska`
  package maintained by Miðeind ehf.
- Build orchestration, conversion, and packaging scripts in this repository are authored
  by repository contributors.

